snippet.title: The Art of Air Guitar Warrior: Environment Medley
snippet.description:
Air Guitar Warrior, releasing on Xbox One on March 29th, features 50 hand-painted levels. Here's a medley showcasing the background art, including (but definitely not limited to) post-apocalyptic ruins, the pits of pandemonium, soaring above mountaintops, the Nevada desert, cyberpunked Ancient Egypt and live stadium shows.
http://airguitarwarrior.com
